ormalfont \selectfont} \DeclareTextFontCommand{	extcyr}{\cyr} \pagestyle{empty} \DeclareMathSizes{10}{9}{7}{6}  egin{document} \landscape $I_{\{ ho ^{u}_{jt+1}< 0\} }$ \end{document} takes a value of unity whenever unexpected excess returns are negative in period \documentclass{aastex} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{bm} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{pifont} \usepackage{stmaryrd} \usepackage{textcomp} \usepackage{portland,xspace} \usepackage{amsmath,amsxtra} \usepackage[OT2,OT1]{fontenc} 
